name: īˈtrakSH(ə)n
description:
īˈtrakSH(ə)n (eyetraction)

“Eye-traction” is a word combination of eye and attraction. It is a visualization of a quality or force of someone or something that tends to pull others in or create interest in the person or thing. Specifically in the visual art. 

This is a collaboration work of Alphabad and Stefany Zefanya. 

Digital & Watercolor
3600 x 3600 px
